-- Anooraq Planning to Double Bokoni Platinum Production, Mining Weekly Says
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-10-08T05:15:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-08/anooraq-planning-to-double-bokoni-platinum-production-mining-weekly-says.html
Anooraq Resources Corp. plans to
double platinum production from its Bokoni mine in South Africa
during the next two years, Mining Weekly reported, citing Chief
Executive Officer Philip Kotze.  The company plans to boost output from the mine, located on
the eastern limb of the Bushveld Complex, to 240,000 ounces per
year by 2013, the Johannesburg-based magazine reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  